    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshicorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s３",
      "startTime": 22.866666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshicorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s３",
      "startTime": 25.6
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_01_01-ngs005.m4a",
      "text": "じじじー……\n……って、あれ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "*stare*\n…Huh?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 25.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_01_01-ngs006.m4a",
      "text": "どこにもいない……\n確かにこっちに来たはずなのに",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Where is he?\nI thought he came this way.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 28.666666666666668,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_01_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "何をしてるんだ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What are you doing?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 31.366666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshicorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s３",
      "startTime": 33.166666666666664
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_01_01-ngs007.m4a",
      "text": "ひゃあっ！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eeek!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 33.166666666666664,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_01_01-ngs008.m4a",
      "text": "じ、自販機の陰に隠れて……？\nどうしてそんな場所にいるんですかっ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Y-you were hiding behind the vending machine?\nWhat were you doing there?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 37.06666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshicorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s３",
      "startTime": 37.06666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_01_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "それを説明するのは渚の方じゃないか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I think you're the one who owes me an explanation‚ Nagisa.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 40.36666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshicorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s３",
      "startTime": 43.6
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_01_01-ngs009.m4a",
      "text": "え、えーっと……\nな、なんの話でしょうかー？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Er‚ well…\nW-what are you talking about?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 45.766666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshicorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s３",
      "startTime": 49.8
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_01_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "いや、今更ごまかすのは無理があるだろう\n今日一日、ずっと俺の後をつけていたよな？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No point trying to hide it.\nYou were following me‚ weren’t you?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 53.80675648152828,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshicorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s３",
      "startTime": 56.9666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_01_01-ngs010.m4a",
      "text": "う……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 57,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshicorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s３",
      "startTime": 58.5
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_01_01-ngs011.m4a",
      "text": "はい、後をつけたりしてごめんなさい……\n悪いことをするつもりはなかったんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah‚ sorry about that…\nI didn’t mean to do anything bad…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 62.46666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_01_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "何か話したいことでもあるのか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Did you want to say something to me?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 65.16666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshicorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s３",
      "startTime": 67.63333333333334
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_01_01-ngs012.m4a",
      "text": "いえ、そういう訳でもないんです\n特に話すことはないというか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No‚ it’s not that…\nThere wasn’t really anything that I wanted to say…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 70,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_01_01-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "えっ……\nそれはそれで傷つくんだが",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh?\nThat‚ er‚ makes me a little sad…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 73.46666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_01_01-ngs013.m4a",
      "text": "あっ、ごめんなさい、ごめんなさい！\n言葉が足りなくて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh! I’m sorry‚ I’m sorry!\nI should have explained myself more clearly…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 78.56666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshicorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s３",
      "startTime": 80.23333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_01_01-ngs014.m4a",
      "text": "実は……私達に見せない\n素の様子を見たかったんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Actually… I wanted to see\nthe side of you that you don’t normally show us.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 82.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshicorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s３",
      "startTime": 85.3
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_01_01-ngs015.m4a",
      "text": "だから、本人に見つかっちゃったら\n意味ないなって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But I guess it’s pointless\nnow that you’ve found out.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 87.63333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_01_01-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "素と言われても……\nこの通り何も変わらないと思うけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m not sure how to answer that…\nNothing really changes‚ as you can see.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 92.83333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshicorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s３",
      "startTime": 96.46666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_01_01-ngs016.m4a",
      "text": "だったらいいんですけど……\n男の人はみんな狼だって言うじゃないですか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I guess… but‚ you know…\nThey say men turn into wolves if you’re not careful‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 98.56666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshicorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s３",
      "startTime": 102.3
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_01_01-ngs017.m4a",
      "text": "もし{user}さんに\n裏の顔があったら大変だから、調査をと思って",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s why I wanted to find out.\nMake sure {user}-san didn’t have a darker side.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 103.2,
