      "text": "本当に琴乃ちゃんを任せていい人なのか\n自分の目でしっかり見極めたくて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I wanted to see with my own eyes\nwhether you were someone I could entrust Kotono-chan to.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 127.06666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshicorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s３",
      "startTime": 129.86666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_01_01-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "なるほど……琴乃とは中学時代からの友達だったな\n随分心配してるんだな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see… Come to think of it‚ the two of you have been friends since middle school.\nYou were concerned for her?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 134.33751388318612,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
