      "text": "はい。琴乃ちゃんのこと\nずっと近くで見てきたので……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes.\nI’ve been watching her up close for a long time.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 139.36666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
