      "text": "理不尽なことで挫折したり\n変なトラブルに巻き込まれたりして欲しくないんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I don’t want her to be frustrated by things out of her control\nor get dragged into trouble.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 143.56666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshicorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s３",
