      "text": "みんなレッスンで毎日忙しいだろ？　それに琴乃は\n積極的に人付き合いをするタイプじゃなさそうだし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ everybody is always busy with lessons.\nAnd Kotono isn’t the kind to actively engage with other people.",
