      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_01_01-koh016.m4a",
      "text": "俺は渚のマネージャーでもあるんだ\n琴乃を気にかけるのもいいが、渚自身もアイドルだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m your manager as well‚ Nagisa.\nIt’s good to hear that you care for Kotono‚ but you’re an idol too.",
